Ayo berkencan.

288
00:19:36,490 --> 00:19:37,859
Itu...

289
00:19:40,159 --> 00:19:41,859
Kita baru bertemu beberapa kali.

290
00:19:41,859 --> 00:19:44,429
Ayolah, angka tidaklah penting.

291
00:19:44,429 --> 00:19:48,169
Aku merasakannya sejak kali pertama melihatmu.

292
00:19:48,730 --> 00:19:50,169
Bagaimana denganmu, Ji Min?

293
00:19:50,800 --> 00:19:53,000
Lihat? Kurasa kamu merasakan hal serupa.

294
00:19:53,810 --> 00:19:56,939
Tunggu, bukankah kamu bilang kamu sangat penakut?

295
00:19:57,280 --> 00:19:58,339
Kenapa kamu tiba-tiba...

296
00:19:58,339 --> 00:20:00,109
Tentu saja tidak, aku seorang pria!

297
00:20:00,609 --> 00:20:02,909
Kalau begitu, mari kita

298
00:20:04,349 --> 00:20:05,520
berkencan.

299
00:20:05,780 --> 00:20:07,820
Mulai sekarang.

300
00:20:08,790 --> 00:20:09,859
Mengerti?

301
00:20:11,419 --> 00:20:12,560
Begini...

302
00:20:13,020 --> 00:20:14,030
Baiklah.

303
00:20:14,990 --> 00:20:15,990
Benarkah?

304
00:20:16,189 --> 00:20:18,530
