437
00:30:51,899 --> 00:30:53,530
Hari apa?

438
00:31:09,480 --> 00:31:11,149
Kurasa itu juga harinya bagiku.

439
00:31:17,260 --> 00:31:18,359
Ada apa?

440
00:31:19,089 --> 00:31:20,389
Kamu tidak bisa berkonsentrasi?

441
00:31:21,429 --> 00:31:22,490
Ya.

442
00:31:24,260 --> 00:31:25,899
